
# 📅 Day 2 – User Research

## 🎯 Objective
Understand the target users of the Food Delivery App and identify their needs before starting the design process.

---

## ✅ Tasks Completed

- Identified the target audience.
- Defined user needs and pain points.
- Created user personas.
- Organized research in Figma.

---

## 👥 Target Users

### 1. Students
- Need affordable meals
- Prefer quick delivery
- Look for discounts and offers

### 2. Working Professionals
- Want fast ordering after work
- Prefer secure online payments
- Need live order tracking

### 3. Families
- Order meals for multiple people
- Prefer combo meals
- Need an easy checkout process

### 4. Busy Individuals
- Want a simple and quick ordering experience
- Prefer one-tap reordering
- Need accurate delivery time

---

# 💡 User Needs

- Easy food search
- Simple navigation
- Secure payment methods
- Live order tracking
- Restaurant ratings and reviews
- Fast checkout
- Order history
- Favorite restaurants

---

